Mobile App Developer Roadmap\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Mobile App Development focuses on building applications for smartphones and tablets, mainly Android and iOS. A Mobile App Developer designs user interfaces, integrates APIs, manages app performance, and publishes apps to app stores.\
This roadmap takes you from basic programming to building and publishing full production mobile applications.\
